            <p><h4>Introduttion</h4> platains chips are a diffrent way of cooking fry platains in a tinner and crushy way</p>

            <p> <h4> ingredients</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>platains</li>
                    <li>cooking oil</li>
                    <li>salt</li>
                    <li>(kepchup is optional) </li>

                </ul>
            
            </p>
            <p><h4>cooking guide</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>cut platains into a thinner and small cuts        </li>
                <li>add the cooking oil to a pan and let heath up</li>
                <li> add cut platians and let cook for 3 minutes the take ot and flatten to chips sides</li>
                <li>add the platains back and fish cooking into crispy brown</li>
                <li>add the salt to finish product and kepchup if like</li>

            </ol>
            
            
            
            
